        Installation
        ------------
        
        Install collective.glossary by adding it to your buildout::
        
            [buildout]
        
            ...
        
            eggs =
                collective.glossary
        
        
        and then running ``bin/buildout``
        
        
        Translations
        ------------
        
        This product has been translated into
        
        - german
        
        
